snippet.title: EDM Tips
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm Will Darling & I'm here to teach you how to produce Electronic Dance Music like a pro! – Techno, House, Trance, Progressive and much, much more.

If you want to seriously "up" your music production game – this is the channel for you.

EDM Tips is all about sharing insanely actionable EDM tips & tutorials that you can use in Ableton Live, FL Studio, Logic X or any other DAW,

Whether you produce House, Future Bass, Trap, Trance or even Pop, you'll pick up some new tips - guaranteed.

I also give away free gifts to my subscribers each week to help them on their music production journey :)

I've been producing dance music for over 25 years – some of which has been Grammy shortlisted as well as hit the number 1 top spot many times on the download charts. My tracks have also had support from many A-List DJs over the years.

If Electronic Dance Music production videos are what you're looking for, make sure to join me each week by subscribing!

Cheers, and happy producing,
Will
